name: SYMME DEMO
description:
This is the story of a gunman for hire, who ends up having to travel back in time to stop himself from ending the world. The game is still in development so I don't want to give too much of the story away.

If you would like to be kept updated on the game's progress, consider subscribing to my YouTube channel https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCfENLQaUQf3t-FD_zVFD-KQ
